sequenceDiagram
    participant Scheduler
    participant Ingestion
    participant CropIntel as Crop Intelligence
    participant Trigger as Trigger Engine
    participant BasisRisk as Basis Risk
    participant Approval
    participant Payout
    participant Notification
    participant Audit

    Scheduler->>Ingestion: Start observation ingestion
    Ingestion->>CropIntel: Clean observations and quality flags
    CropIntel->>Trigger: Crop stage and expected NDVI
    Trigger->>Trigger: Evaluate Trigger A/B/C
    Trigger->>Audit: Append trigger event decision
    Trigger->>BasisRisk: Evaluate basis-risk rules
    BasisRisk->>Approval: Route to auto approval or review
    Approval->>Payout: Approve payout creation
    Payout->>Audit: Append payout record state
    Payout->>Notification: Queue farmer/internal notification
    Notification->>Audit: Append delivery state
